{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act32side", "eventName": "水晶箭行動", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "CR-4", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "非傳統藝術空間", "storyInfo": "藝術節上將要展出的大木偶發生了故障，虹彩小隊與特克諾合力將其解決。起舞木偶的第一次彩排震撼了在場所有人的心。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_windows", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$suspenseful_intro", "key": "$suspenseful_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來特克諾已經穿戴好安全設備了，看她抓耳朵的樣子，根本不像是準備好了。", "name": "FUZE"}, "figure_art": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在下去？", "name": "FUZE"}, "figure_art": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "稍等，等她下降到既定位置，我可不想在速降過程中發生衝撞。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sldrsldng", "channel": "1"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "1"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸欸欸，慢點慢點，我掉得太快了！！", "name": "特克諾"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這也算快嗎？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#10$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她就像片小羽毛，緩緩落下。", "name": "FUZE"}, "figure_art": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……現在可不是笑到肚子痛的好時候。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她到位置了。", "name": "FUZE"}, "figure_art": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一切就緒，你也可以動身了。", "name": "FUZE"}, "figure_art": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "扯扯手中的安全繩，ELA側身翻出窗戶，將腳尖抵在牆上，努力讓懸空的身體在風中保持住平衡。"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等了一下子，風漸漸停下，她鬆開一隻抓住繩子的手，將被風吹歪的帽子戴正，向屋內的FUZE露出微笑。"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隨後，她將另一隻手也鬆開，消失在窗外，只留下一段繩索掛在窗沿快速滑動。"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sldrsldng"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……不錯，看來她們是成功會晤了。", "name": "FUZE"}, "figure_art": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "38_g20_skyblue_R1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sldrsldng"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "posfrom": "0,25", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇啊啊啊——！你怎麼也跳下來了！", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#4$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別吵，專注點，剛才你差點就要剪斷一條主操作線了。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些跟著你的人呢？", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#5$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "甩掉了。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老爹難道沒有警告過你不要到處亂走嗎……", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#5$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，說了。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你還跟過來幹什麼？", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "確保你不會搞砸這項工程。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#8$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這人……你知道該怎麼辦嗎，就這麼講我？", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你呢？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#8$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃……", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下降時我簡單檢查了一下木偶手臂上的控制元件，是液壓驅動的問題，把你的工具給我。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_windows", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們就在上面，快點！", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要不是底下那個女人攔著，早就逮捕他們了……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嚯……", "name": "FUZE"}, "figure_art": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看起來之後都是我的麻煩了。", "name": "FUZE"}, "figure_art": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g9_gangsters", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "領隊！好消息，繩索交纏的地方解開了！", "name": "作業人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1274_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼快？那趕快把特克諾拉上來，我們繼續組裝木偶的手臂與身體。", "name": "指揮人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1274_1#1$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她說她要繼續留在那裡。", "name": "作業人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1274_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？", "name": "指揮人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1274_1#1$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說我要繼續待在這裡！我會在這裡輔助安裝！", "name": "特克諾"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1274_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，你願意幫忙當然很好，可你能保證不會影響到旁邊的ELA女士嗎？", "name": "指揮人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1274_1#1$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你再說一次？我等一下上去要一拳揍歪你的鼻子！", "name": "特克諾"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1274_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳，ELA小姐，為了我的鼻子著想，你能讓她繼續留在那裡嗎？", "name": "指揮人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1274_1#1$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然可以，特克諾小姐是個講義氣的朋友，不願意讓我一個人面對高空作業的危險。除了感激，我還能說什麼呢？", "name": "ELA"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳、咳！", "name": "特克諾"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g8_slums", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看，木偶的手臂重新開始移動了！", "name": "驚訝的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那裡吊著的人是特克諾……怎麼還有另外一個人？", "name": "驚訝的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是誰？工程師，技師，還是特克諾的助手？", "name": "疑惑的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "助手，你確定？特克諾一向不喜歡有人參與到她的設計中來。", "name": "驚訝的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我再看看……不行，視線被擋住了。欸，朋友，你能認出來嗎？", "name": "疑惑的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在問我嗎？", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#1$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對，你站在那邊仰頭看了好一下子了。你能看清特克諾旁邊的人是誰嗎？", "name": "疑惑的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你問ELA？事情有點複雜——", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#7$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，是我看錯了嗎？這傢伙居然拍了拍特克諾的腦袋……上次這麼做的人差點被她咬掉一根手指。", "name": "驚訝的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_416_1#1$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，所以你們就當她是特克諾的……朋友吧？", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#10$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_windows", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1215_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-100,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-100,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1215_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可惡，你這傢伙溜得還挺快。", "name": "社區守衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1215_1#1$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_punch", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "action": "jump", "posto": "100,0", "power": 40.0, "times": 1.0, "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 40.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "action": "jump", "posto": "100,0", "power": 20.0, "times": 1.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔……", "name": "FUZE"}, "figure_art": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1215_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，是條漢子，挨了我這一拳還能不聲不響的。", "name": "社區守衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1215_1#1$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快點把路讓開，你也不想今天就交待在這裡吧？", "name": "社區守衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1215_1#1$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1215_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊啊啊——！！", "name": "特克諾"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1215_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特克諾，堅持住，我們馬上就來，那女人休想動你一根汗毛！", "name": "社區守衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1215_1#1$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1215_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "把手拿開！你這女人想要幹什麼！", "name": "特克諾"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1215_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這傢伙快給我從窗戶邊閃開！", "name": "社區守衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1215_1#1$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_punch02"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "100,0", "posto": "200,0", "duration": 0.8}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "100,0", "posto": "200,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "250,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1215_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "200,0", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特克諾，你還好嗎？！", "name": "社區守衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1215_1#1$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1215_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "200,0", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你、你怎麼在上面？", "name": "特克諾"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1215_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "200,0", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老爹派我來盯著那些外來的傢伙，我聽到你的慘叫了，那女人對你做了什麼？！我這就爬下來幫你！", "name": "社區守衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1215_1#1$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1215_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "200,0", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，沒、沒事，我挺好的，就是……就是……", "name": "特克諾"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我剛剛拍了她的腦袋。", "name": "ELA"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1215_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "200,0", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "力道很重？", "name": "社區守衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1215_1#1$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1215_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "200,0", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有……", "name": "特克諾"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1215_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "200,0", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……那你喊什麼？", "name": "社區守衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1215_1#1$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1215_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "200,0", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……呃，那個總之我沒事，你們回去告訴老爹，讓他放心，我看著這女人，不會出事的。", "name": "特克諾"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特克諾，把焊接工具遞給我，謝了。", "name": "ELA"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "給，在這裡。", "name": "特克諾"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1215_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "200,0", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）這丫頭居然甘心當人助手……", "name": "社區守衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1215_1#1$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老兄，既然她兩能合作得親密無間，你還有什麼疑問嗎？", "name": "FUZE"}, "figure_art": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g9_gangsters", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "木偶已經組裝完成了，領隊！", "name": "作業人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1274_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼……準備好了嗎？朋友們，我們來到最難的一關了。", "name": "指揮人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1274_1#1$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "給她們心跳，給她們血液，給她們活力，給她們生命。", "name": "指揮人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1274_1#1$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已經準備很久了，領隊，請下達命令吧。", "name": "作業人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1274_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "各位，歷經大半年的付出與努力，我們最終還是克服種種困難來到了這一天，感激大家的堅持……", "name": "指揮人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1274_1#1$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "各部門請聽好，第一次起舞測驗準備開始。", "name": "指揮人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1274_1#1$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來吧，女孩們，眨眨眼。", "name": "指揮人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1274_1#1$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g8_slums", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_242"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rampartclose", "channel": "1"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.8, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……她們醒了。", "name": "社區居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我曾經無數次地想像過這個畫面。", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#4$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "傳單上，每個人的講述中，草稿圖紙上……這很難實現，所以我接受她們與我的想像有出入，我接受她們無法滿足我的幻想。", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#4$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在呢？你親眼見到了。", "name": "社區居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只能說……這一切遠超我的想像。", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#4$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看著那兩個正在不停眨眼的巨大木偶，IANA再次被她們的美麗面容與精細構造震撼到了。"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一動不動坐在那裡時，她們是兩件漂亮的藝術品，但當她們動起來，就是這裡最美麗的兩個女孩。"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她們濃密的睫毛抬起來，然後迅速垂下去，擋住了眼睛，IANA幾次嘗試去看也沒能看到。"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "突然，她們中的一個低下頭轉向IANA，低垂的睫毛抬起後再沒有落下來，目光對上IANA的視線。"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是一雙橙紅色的瞳孔。"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的眼睛為什麼是橙紅色？", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#1$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是朝陽倒映在她眼中的顏色，她會在陽光下盡情舞蹈。", "name": "社區居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，是陽光將它染成了橙紅色……", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#1$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原本我們想做一對黑色的眼珠，你懂，全塗黑很省事。但是特克諾不願意，她覺得黑色是最不受陽光青睞的顏色。", "name": "社區居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……不，她說錯了。", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#1$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陽光不會青睞的顏色其實是白色。", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#7$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在掌聲與歡呼聲中，木偶開始伸展自己的四肢，每個關節的活動，都需要一群人拼盡全力，嘶吼著拉扯牽繩。"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g9_gangsters", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1274_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我數一，二，三！拉！", "name": "指揮人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1274_1#1$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃啊————！", "name": "作業人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rampartclose", "channel": "1"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.8, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "木偶抬起膝蓋，向前邁出一步。"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1274_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，諸位，一，二，三，放！", "name": "指揮人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1274_1#1$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦呀————！", "name": "作業人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rampartclose", "channel": "1"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.8, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "木偶揮動手臂，輕輕擦過身側。"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1274_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，一，二，三，再來一次！", "name": "指揮人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1274_1#1$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗬啊————————！", "name": "作業人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沿著圍觀者讓開的道路，她們以輕快的步伐穿過居民樓，偶爾矮下身通過兩棟樓之間的連廊。"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後她們停在了社區的中央廣場上。"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_windows", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一，二，三！呃啊——！", "name": "FUZE"}, "figure_art": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown1"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝了，朋友。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#8$1"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你要換個地方欣賞這場表演嗎？", "name": "FUZE"}, "figure_art": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1"}, {"id": 380, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用了，這個窗戶的觀景效果不錯。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#8$1"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我看看時間，嗯，差不多快到了。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#8$1"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g8_slums", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天色逐漸暗沉，雙月漸漸從城市的遠端升起，月光將水泥地照得像冬日結冰的湖面。"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩位木偶舞者在地面上旋轉，隨著響板的節奏聲，她們的身體或繃直，或蜷曲，每一寸曲線都在月光下盡情展示。"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從高樓中，屋簷下，小巷裡，還有幾扇昏暗的窗戶間，樂聲傾瀉而出。"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是一場即興的合奏，沒有排演，沒有指揮。"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "樂聲只是隨著木偶舞者的舞步肆意地流淌。"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而舞者挪移間飛起的裙擺也在不停捕捉著流至她們腳下的音符，並將其轉換為美妙的舞動。"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "高大的木偶低下頭顱，注視著那些在她們腳邊的人。"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些如同羽粉一般輕盈細小的人，跟著她們的舞步。"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在空氣中跳躍，然後落地。"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_windows", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你現在還覺得我不理智嗎？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#8$1"}, {"id": 412, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（搖頭）", "name": "FUZE"}, "figure_art": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1"}, {"id": 414, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很值得。", "name": "FUZE"}, "figure_art": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1"}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你早就預見到了這樣的場景對嗎？所以才願意盡心去幫他們。", "name": "FUZE"}, "figure_art": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1"}, {"id": 416, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我從來沒有那樣預先設想過，那不是樂趣所在。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#9$1"}, {"id": 418, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "33_g8_srcroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，真棒，是誰教你吹口琴的？", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 430, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_240"}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是媽媽，媽媽什麼都會，會吹口琴，會跳舞，會畫畫，還會烤很好吃的可頌麵包。", "name": "稚嫩的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我最喜歡媽媽了！", "name": "稚嫩的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 435, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然很敬佩那位無所不能的女士，但我還是要說，應該唸Croissant！", "name": "DOC"}, "figure_art": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#5$1"}, {"id": 440, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_240"}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……Quaso？", "name": "稚嫩的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 444, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#5", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈哈哈哈——！", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#5"}, {"id": 449, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼……算了。", "name": "DOC"}, "figure_art": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#9$1"}, {"id": 451, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我得來杯咖啡。", "name": "DOC"}, "figure_art": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#7$1"}, {"id": 453, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 454, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 455, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 456, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 457, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 458, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ltroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 459, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 460, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$darkness_03_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 461, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 462, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 463, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 464, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雷內爾先生，我仔細檢查了一番音樂盒，徹底修復需要花費幾週的時間。", "name": "修復師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1"}, {"id": 465, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但目前，我先按照夾層內的樂譜重製了一小部分音筒，您要試聽一下嗎？", "name": "修復師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1"}, {"id": 466, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 467, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}, {"id": 468, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 469, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 470, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一段悠揚的音樂從盒中傾瀉而出，將雷內爾的回憶帶到十多年前的午後，他貼在門後，偷聽從母親工坊裡傳出的叮噹聲。"}}, {"id": 471, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 472, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "光憑這一小段修復的曲子推測，應該是一首搖籃曲。", "name": "修復師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1"}, {"id": 473, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 474, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……很樸實的曲子。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1"}, {"id": 475, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 476, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，所以初次聽到時我覺得很驚訝，我記得在以往的作品中，您母親使用的旋律往往是精美的名家之作。", "name": "修復師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1"}, {"id": 477, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 478, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為這首曲子是她自己寫的……", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1"}, {"id": 479, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 480, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……她不是專業的作曲家，只是作為一個母親，為她的孩子寫下了這首並不出彩的搖籃曲。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#2$1"}, {"id": 481, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有什麼特別之處。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#2$1"}, {"id": 482, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 483, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但至少對於那個孩子來說，它是特別的。", "name": "修復師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1"}, {"id": 484, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 485, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1"}, {"id": 486, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 487, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雷內爾先生……您一直盯著窗外，那裡有什麼？", "name": "修復師"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1"}, {"id": 488, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 489, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"s